->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"http://52.203.180.0/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot_20230301-194520_Gallery-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-74\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></figure>\n<!-- /wp:gallery --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mi Nombre es Antonio, soy Administrador de Sistemas Informáticos, y un apasionado de la Cocina. Mi sueño es mezclar estos 2 conceptos que mas me gustan en mi vida .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Esta pagina es el inicio de mi proyecto, una pagina donde poder compartir recetas e ideas para la cocine, y ayude a la gente de una forma mas sencilla que con libros o recetas que necesiten instrumentos muy avanzados.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\">Saber Mas...</a></div>\n<!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','','','inherit','closed','closed','','62-revision-v1','','','2023-11-06 08:33:52','2023-11-06 08:33:52','',62,'http://52.203.180.0/wordpress/?p=75',0,'revision','',0),(79,1,'2023-11-06 08:40:55','2023-11-06 08:40:55','{\n    \"yummy-bites::sidebar_width\": {\n        \"value\": \"0\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2023-11-06 08:40:14\"\n    },\n    \"yummy-bites::ed_social_links\": {\n        \"value\": true,\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2023-11-06 08:40:14\"\n    },\n    \"yummy-bites::no_of_slides\": {\n        \"value\": \"5\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2023-11-06 08:40:55\"\n    }\n}','','','trash','closed','closed','','de