>\n            <p>This will make the perfect dish for your Christmas Morning Brunch! Looking for some other great Christmas Morning Recipes? We have tons!!</p>','The Best Instant Pot French Toast recipe (vegan &amp; Gluten Free!)','Love French Toast Casserole, but don’t time to let it sit overnight? Not to worry, with this Instant Pot French Toast will be ready in no time!','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2023-11-06 08:42:11','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://52.203.180.0/wordpress/?p=82',0,'recipe','',0),(83,1,'2023-11-06 08:42:11','2023-11-06 08:42:11','','dummy-recipe-img','','inherit','open','closed','','dummy-recipe-img','','','2023-11-06 08:42:11','2023-11-06 08:42:11','',82,'http://52.203.180.0/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/dummy-recipe-img.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(84,1,'2023-11-06 08:42:11','2023-11-06 08:42:11','','Tipos de plato de receta','','trash','closed','closed','','tipos-de-plato-de-receta__trashed','','','2023-11-08 08:07:06','2023-11-08 08:07:06','',0,'http://52.203.180.0/wordpress/index.php/tipos-de-plato-de-receta/',0,'page','',0),(85,1,'2023-11-06 08:42:11','2023-11-06 08:42:11','','Métodos de cocinado de receta','','trash','closed','closed','','metodos-de-cocinado-de-receta__trashed','','','2023-11-08 08:07:05','2023-11-08 08:07:05','',0,'http://52.203.180.0/wordpress/index.php/metodos-de-cocinado-de-receta/',0,'page','',0),(86,1,'2023-11-06 08:42:11','2023-11-06 08:42:11','','Cocinas de receta','','trash','closed','closed','','cocinas-de-receta__trashed','','','2023-11-08 08:07:05','2023-11-08 08:07:05','',0,'http://52.203.180.0/wordpress/index.php/cocinas-de-receta/',0,'page','',0),(87,1,'2023-11-06 08:42:11','2023-11-06 08:42:11','','Claves de receta','','trash','closed','closed','','claves-de-receta__trashed','','','2023-11-08 08:07:05','2023-11-08 08:07:05','',0,'http://52.203.180.0/wordpress/index.php/claves-de-receta/',0,'page','',0),(88,1,'2023-11-06 08:42:11','2023-11-06 08:42:11','','Etiquetas de receta',''